OL,3,CStride: Tories would abolish business
OL,4,Crates tax in overhaul to UK finances
OL,6,FThe Conservatives will abolish
OL,7,Fbusiness rates for high street shops
OL,8,Fand pubs if they win the next
OL,9,Felection, the shadow chancellor has
OL,10,Fpromised.
OL,12,FSpeaking at the second day of the
OL,13,FConservative Party conference in
OL,14,FManchester, Stride announced the
OL,15,FTories would abolish the business
OL,16,Frates and would also offer a #5,000
OL,17,Fnational insurance rebate for people
OL,18,Fgetting their first full-time job
