OL,3,CStride: Tories would abolish business
OL,4,Crates tax in overhaul to UK finances
OL,6,FMaking the case for "Conservative
OL,7,Fvalues," Stride set out plans to
OL,8,Fdramatically shrink the welfare state,
OL,9,Fsaving #23 billion in the process.
OL,11,FHe promised, under a Conservative
OL,12,Fgovernment, benefits would no longer
OL,13,Fbe paid to people with "less severe
OL,14,Fmental health problems," claiming
OL,15,F"stability, pride and social
OL,16,Finteraction of work actually improves
OL,17,Fthese conditions."
