OL,3,CStride: Tories would abolish business
OL,4,Crates tax in overhaul to UK finances
OL,6,FThe shadow chancellor also set out
OL,7,Fplans previously trailed to remove
OL,8,Fbenefits from non-British citizens,
OL,9,Falthough the Conservatives had already
OL,10,Fconceded prior to Stride's speech this
OL,11,Fwould not include those with EU
OL,12,Fsettled status.
OL,14,FFurther savings would be made under
OL,15,Fthe Conservatives' plans by reducing
OL,16,Fthe size of the civil service by
OL,17,Faround one quarter, and reducing the
OL,18,Foverseas aid budget to 0.1% amounting
OL,19,Fto #8 and #7 billion in savings
OL,20,Frespectively.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
