OL,3,CStride: Tories would abolish business
OL,4,Crates tax in overhaul to UK finances
OL,6,FCuts would also be made through
OL,7,Feliminating the use of asylum hotels,
OL,8,Fsomething both Labour and Reform have
OL,9,Falso committed to, and ending "vanity
OL,10,Fprojects," with Stride taking aim at
OL,11,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband and his
OL,12,Fenvironmental policies in particular.
OL,14,F"No more pretending we can keep
OL,15,Fspending money we simply do not have,"
OL,16,Fsaid Stride.
OL,18,FStride did make some spending
OL,19,Fannouncements however, all with the
OL,20,Faim of boosting growth.
