OL,3,CStride: Tories would abolish business
OL,4,Crates tax in overhaul to UK finances
OL,6,FHis headline announcement being the
OL,7,Fabolition of business rates for shops
OL,8,Fand pubs on high streets.
OL,10,F"End of, finished, gone," said Stride.
OL,12,F"Controlling spending is not an end in
OL,13,Fitself, it wills the means, it gets
OL,14,Fthe taxman off your back ` it sets
OL,15,Fsome of the hardest working people in
OL,16,Four country free!
OL,18,F"We can and we will," he finished.
