OL,6,F"The Conservative Party will never,
OL,7,Fever make fiscal commitments without
OL,8,Fspelling out exactly how they will be
OL,9,Fpaid for," Stride promised.
OL,11,FThe #47 billion of cuts seemingly
OL,12,Fcover these commitments, but how
OL,13,Frelevant they will still be in four
OL,14,Fyear's time is a question for the next
OL,15,Fparty conference - of which there are
OL,16,Fat least three before they could even
OL,17,Fthink of taking office.
